## ğŸ¤¹ Platform Grammar (v1)

| Construct | Function | Description | Student Relationship |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Space** | Identity Field | A node of affiliation, community, or orbit | â€œThis is where I belong or observeâ€ |
| **Signal** | Microexpression | A small action with high interpretive value (RSVP, repost, react) | â€œThis matters to meâ€”even if I donâ€™t say whyâ€ |
| **Cluster** | Emergent Grouping | A dynamic network formed by behavior overlap (shared follows, same Spaces) | â€œThese are people like meâ€ |
| **Pulse** | Energy Snapshot | A moment or topic that is vibrating through campus | â€œThis is whatâ€™s hot right nowâ€ |
| **Trail** | Memory Thread | A userâ€™s evolving footprint through participation and creation | â€œThis is how I got hereâ€ |
| **Gathering** | Coordinated Energy | A time-bound event, meetup, or moment | â€œWeâ€™re converging around thisâ€ |
| **Gravity** | Network Pull | The invisible force that draws users toward certain Spaces or content | â€œI keep seeing thisâ€”itâ€™s pulling me inâ€ |
| **Boost** | Signal Amplification | A way to increase visibility or momentum within the network | â€œThis deserves more attentionâ€ |
| **Role** | Structural Function | A userâ€™s defined position within a Space or cluster (creator, member, observer) | â€œThis is how I show up hereâ€ |
| **Vibe** | Social Feel | The soft signal or tone of a Space, post, or event | â€œThis feels like my energyâ€ |

