| Friend action nearby | Show â€œFriend Motionâ€ card | Network proximity awareness |

---

## **ğŸ§© Cold Start Strategy**

- Pre-seed Feed with real events from public org database
- Pre-load Spaces from org list + ritual tags
- Show Friend Motion even without actual graph via proximity inference
- Ritual Strip drives first interaction within 15s
- Feed uses hover + tap data from first session to adjust curation on day 2

