## **ğŸ§± FEED BODY (VERTICAL MOTION STACK)**

### **Card Types & Behavior:**

### **ğŸ“… Event Card**

- Title, time, location
- RSVP button (tap = logs, no modal)
- Tap = detail
- Long-press (Verified+) = Boost

### **ğŸ” Repost Card**

- â€œLaney reposted...â€
- Original Event or Drop shown
- Tap = view source
- Repost chain possible

### **ğŸ’¬ Quote Card**

- â€œLaney: â€˜bring snacksâ€™â€
- Tap = event or source Space
- Requote not available in v1

### **ğŸ¯ Ritual Card**

- Campus-wide ritual prompt
- Tap = full-screen Ritual interaction
- Completion logs Trail, may resurface in Feed as echo

### **ğŸš€ Space Suggestion**

- â€œDesign Union just got activeâ€
- Tap = view Space
- â€œJoinâ€ = logs Trail, changes Feed logic

### **ğŸ‘€ Friend Motion**

- â€œYou and 2 others just viewed thisâ€
- Tap = event or Space
- Names hidden unless Verified+ and public

