# **ğŸŸª PHASE 5B â€” SPACES**

**Section:** UX Surfaces â†’ Logic â†’ Data

**Status:** âœ… Finalized

---

## **ğŸ§  CORE PURPOSE**

A **Space** is a public-facing, motion-responsive container that reflects affiliation, social momentum, and student-driven identity.

Spaces are not chat rooms, they are not static groups â€” they are live micro-networks. Every action taken in a Space contributes to the systemâ€™s network memory, social mapping, and motion architecture.

---

## **ğŸ“² UX SURFACE (LIST-BASED STRUCTURE)**

**All Spaces use a vertical scroll format** with structured behavioral sections. Everything is modular.

### **ğŸ” Top Section**

- **Name + Tags**
    
    â†’ Always visible. Tags pulled from public data or Builder-entered.
    
    â†’ Tap tag = see similar Spaces.
    
- **Join Button**
    
    â†’ Students can view everything before joining
    
    â†’ Joining is required to interact with Drops or Prompts
    
    â†’ Logs to Trail + unlocks social motion
    
- **Member Scroll**
    
    â†’ Avatars only (priority to Verified+, Builder)
    
    â†’ No follower counts
    
    â†’ Tap avatar = Profile (if public)
    

---

### **ğŸ“„ Behavioral Content Stack (Card Modules)**

Cards surface based on motion and system thresholds. No static ordering â€” most alive = top.

| **Card** | **Visibility** | **Interaction** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Upcoming Event** | All users | RSVP, view detail |
| **Active Prompt** | All users | Members only can vote |
| **Drop Stream (1-liners)** | All users | Members only can post |
| **Most Quoted Drop** | All users | Tap = view quotes |
| **Join Momentum Summary** | All users | View-only |
| **Past Prompt Results** | All users | View-only |
| **Reposts with Quote** | All users | View-only, link to Feed |

---

## **â„ï¸ COLD-START CONTENT SOURCES**

If the Builder has not yet engaged:

- Events can be **pre-seeded** via public org calendar
- System may generate **default Drop**: *â€œThis org is live on HIVE â€” join to start motion.â€*
- **Join activity** auto-triggers â€œ3 students joined this weekâ€ card
- Feed-adjacent quotes pull into Space for visibility

---

## **ğŸ” PERMITTED INTERACTIONS (ALL ROLES)**

| **Action** | **Requires Join?** | **Affects Feed?** | **Affects Trail?** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| View Drops / Events / Prompts | âŒ | âœ… indirectly | âœ… silently |
| Join Space | âœ… | âœ… (suggestion, trail heat) | âœ… |
| RSVP to Event | âŒ | âœ… | âœ… |
| Drop (1-liner post) | âœ… | âœ… (if tapped/quoted) | âœ… |
| Quote Event or Drop | âœ… | âœ… | âœ… |
| Vote on Prompt | âœ… | âœ… (if threshold hit) | âœ… |
| Boost (Builder-only) | âœ… | âœ… prominently | âœ… |

---

## **ğŸ” ROLES & PERMISSIONS**

| **Role** | **Set By** | **Powers** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Public | - | View-only |
| Member | Self-join | Drop, Vote, RSVP |
| Verified+ | System | Visible badge, feeds into discovery |
| Builder | System/Manual | Can create Events, Prompts, Boost content |

