## **ğŸ§© FEATURE + FUNCTIONALITY INVENTORY**

### **ğŸ“Œ Auth & Identity**

- Join Space
- View Tags + Description
- View members
- View Verified+ and Builder visibly

### **ğŸ“… Events**

- View + RSVP
- Avatar RSVP stack
- Repost or Quote to Feed

### **âœï¸ Drops (Posts)**

- Add 1-liner (members only)
- View all
- Quote to Feed
- React (in future, low-friction)

### **ğŸ—³ï¸ Prompts**

- Vote on builder-created prompt
- View real-time or archived results

### **ğŸ§ª Single-Player Features**

- View-only Trail logging
- Watch Mode (Space influences Feed w/o join)
- Soft bookmark (Save silently)
- Drop drafts (private)
- Tap-tracking (Drop heat detection)

