## **ğŸ”„ SPACE STATE ENGINE**

| **State** | **Trigger** | **System Behavior** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Hidden | Created, no join or motion | Not discoverable |
| Forming | â‰¥3 joins or 1 motion | Appears in search |
| Live | â‰¥10 joins and recent activity | Feed-suggestible |
| Dormant | 7d of inactivity | UI collapses, search deprioritized |
| Legacy | Archived manually or auto-faded (30d+) | Read-only, Trail visible |

---

## **ğŸ¯ SPACE IS FUNCTIONAL WHEN...**

- A student can join, view, or interact with motion in < 10s
- Feed and Trail reflect behavior (even passive)
- Builders aren't required for motion to begin
- Cold-started orgs still surface meaningful value
- Everything inside a Space feeds back into system
- Spaces decay cleanly if unused

# **PHASE 5C â€” PROFILE**

**Section:** UX Surfaces â†’ Logic â†’ Data

**Status:** âœ… Finalized

---

## **ğŸ§  CORE PURPOSE**

The Profile is not a resume, not a feed, not a bio.

It is a **reflection of motion** â€” who you are *based on what you do across the system*.

It should feel earned, living, and ambient.

Not constructed, performative, or fixed.

---

## **ğŸ¯ PRIMARY FUNCTIONS**

| **Function** | **Description** |
| --- | --- |
| Identity | Who is this student in the context of campus life? |
| Presence | What are they involved in *right now*? |
| Memory | What has shaped them inside HIVE? |
| Access | What do they unlock (Verified, Builder, Rituals)? |
| Social Mapping | What Spaces are they orbiting, what roles have they played? |

---

## **ğŸ“² UX STRUCTURE (LIST + LAYERED MODULAR CARDS)**

Profile is scrollable, non-interactive beyond view and light surfacing.

### **ğŸ” Top Section (Fixed)**

- **Avatar** (editable)
- **Name / Display handle**
- **Status Badge**
    - Public
    - Verified (.edu)
    - Verified+ (student leader)
- **Role Context** (Builder in X Spaces)
- **Bio (Optional)** â†’ Max 150 characters

---

### **ğŸ§  Modular Sections (Conditionally Shown)**

Each card appears only if youâ€™ve triggered it. No filler, no forced layout.

### **ğŸ”¹ Current Spaces (Affiliation)**

- â€œCurrently active in 3 Spacesâ€
- Avatars of Spaces (tappable)
- Sorted by most recent activity

### **ğŸ”¹ Motion Summary (Trail Snippets)**

- â€œLast 30 days: 2 Drops, 1 RSVP, 1 Prompt votedâ€
- Auto-generated
- Not editable
- Visible only if threshold of activity is met

### **ğŸ”¹ Badge Showcase (System-Wide Rituals Only)**

- â€œEarned during Campus Madnessâ€
- Badges are not user-claimable
- System-assigned via Rituals only
- Max 3 shown at a time

### **ğŸ”¹ Builder Credential**

- â€œBuilder of [Space Name]â€
- Tap = view Space
- Only appears if active in last 14d

### **ğŸ”¹ Legacy Trail (Deep Echoes)**

- â€œFirst joined during Fall Launch Weekâ€
- â€œTop Drop was quoted 12x in UB Creativesâ€
- Memory-style summarizations (system-generated)
- Optional visibility toggle (default: private)

---

## **ğŸ” VISIBILITY MODEL**

| **Section** | **Visible to Public** | **Visible to Verified** | **Notes** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Avatar + Badge | âœ… | âœ… | Always visible |
| Trail Summary | âŒ | âœ… | Optional toggle on |
| Spaces | âœ… | âœ… | Based on join visibility |
| Builder Status | âœ… | âœ… | Shown only if active |
| Legacy Trail | âŒ | âœ… | Summarized only after activity milestones |
